2: Secondary assist(on raids) / Nuke in group.<br>
3: Another Nuke.<br>
4: Damageshield.<br>
5: /pet Back off.<br>
6: /pet Kill.<br>
7: Tinker Bag with robes.<br>
8: Jboots.<br>
9: Chest slot.<br>
10: Box of Nil Space with all kinds of right click items.<br>
<br>
Page 2:<br>
1: Sit<br>
2: Spellbook<br>
3: Malosini<br>
5: /pet back off<br>
6: /pet kill<br>
<br>
Nothing more interesting stuff, I got just about everything possible under a key somewhere, but these I use all the time.<br>
Key #5 and #6 are the same on all 10 pages so I can always back off pet with one button.<br>
I don't really have more reason as to why the keys are on that position, I just placed them there at some point and used them.<br>
<br>
