<br>
1 - Sit/Stand<br>
2 - Assist1<br>
3 - /pet follow me<br>
4 - /pet guard here<br>
5 - /pet attack<br>
6 - /pet back off<br>
7 - /pet report health<br>
8 - CoH emote macro<br>
9 - Malosi emote macro<br>
0 - Annul Magic emote macro<br>
<br>
I use ALT-# to cast spells, not hotkeys.  Just as fast for me to do that that hit a single number.  My normal spells memmed are:<br>
<br>
1 - Wrath of the Elements (since most mobs at my lvl last more than 30 secs, I can cast this, sit and med for 30 secs before resuming nuking)<br>
2 - Char (most places I fight, I can't get clear line of sight for Lava Bolt or Scars of Sigil)<br>
3 - Malosi<br>
4 - Pet of the Day (normally L54 water, sometimes L51 earth)<br>
5 - Gate<br>
6 - Call of the Hero<br>
7 - Burnout 3 (until I get burnout 4)<br>
8 - Damage Shield<br>
<br>
Hope this helps you some.<br>
