<br>
1(the 1 key) - /pet attack<br>
2(the 2 key) - sit<br>
3(the 3 key) - /pet back off<br>
4(the 4 key) - Malosini<br>
5(the 5 key) - Char or Shock of Steel<br>
6(the q key) - /pet guard here (or coh when in pull group)<br>
7(the w key) - /pet follow me<br>
8(the 8 key) - Spells<br>
9(the 9 key) - Persona<br>
10(the num pad 0 key) - /assist <br>
<br>
q and w are nice keys to configure because they are right below the 1 and 2 keys.  The num pad 0 key is nice because it's positioned right next to the direction arrows.  A quick tap with my right pinky and I'm on target, the left hand then does all my commands. <p><A HREF="http://sr.amiga.tm/" TARGET="_new"><IMG ALT="Silent Redemption Member" BORDER=0 SRC="http://fairblade.sinbad.net/images/SRlogo.gif"></A><BR><BR> Zellis the Conjurer<BR> 59 Conjurer<BR> Silent Redemption<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uluymen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Luymen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#333333>(4/5/01 6:06:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=43.topic&index=27>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: .</span><hr size=1> Here's mine at 40th:<br>
