<br>
Make a social containing the following lines and hotkey it:<br>
/pet taunt off<br>
/pet back off<br>
/pet back off<br>
/pet back off<br>
/pet back off<br>
<br>
Now, we normally want to have /pet taunt ON to have him get mobs off of us and the clerics/enchanters etc. but this can be typed or hotkeyed on page 2 or something. However, when we suddenly need to get Goner to back off, we hit one key and it turns taunt off and gives 4 quick shots at getting him to back off. Now granted, I'll still be hammering away at this hotkey but this way we've got 2 commands combined here and, we don't have to give ourselves carpal tunnel syndrome from trying to smash this key at Mach 4. (This should also prolong the life of your keyboard &gt;-} )<br>
<br>
If anyone has the chance to try this, please let us know how it works. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=panick>panick</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#333333>(12/4/01 12:06:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=43.topic&index=29>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: my 2cp :)</span><hr size=1> add /loc and /doability 1 (sense heading)<br>
