 just going thru the 1st bank<br>
<br>
hk1= spells( i play in full screen)<br>
hk2= /pet attack with an emote so peeps can see what i am doing<br>
hk3=primary bolt type nuke<br>
hk4=primary non bolt nuke (shock series)<br>
hk5=elemental malestrom i like it in case of adds when i have to chain cast pets alot less aggro then nukes<br>
hk6=sit<br>
hk7=damage shield<br>
hk8=malise,malisement,or malosi<br>
hk9=/pet back off with an emote so folks no what i am doing<br>
hk10=/assist<br>
<br>
i hot key spells so i can use the socials as another set of hotkeys with the mouse (it takes me 2 hands for alt# or i have to think about it longer than i should)<br>
<br>
usually keep memmend<br>
<br>
1=gate<br>
